# Render: vhs assets/demo/without-precept.tape
# Output:  assets/demo/without-precept.gif

Output assets/demo/without-precept.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 900
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms
Set Padding 24

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 600ms
Type "bash assets/demo/scripts/without-precept.sh"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 18s
